data.description: Welcome to Rolling Hills. Beautifully Upgraded Home with No Neighbors behind, NO MELLO & LOW HOA. Within a great schools district, Easy Access freeway, along with Restaurants, Shopping Mall, and more. There is a Community Pool, Parks, Walking Trails & more.  2 car garage detached and a unique courtyard. The house does have solar, they are leased. Move in ready. Call Today!
